                        <interp inst="t18640411-name-309" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ALLEN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman,</hi> 242). I took the prisoner—he said that he knew nothing about it—I took him to Smithfield station, and found a waist-coat</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186404110061"></xptr>
               <p>doubled up under his coat—it was not worn—the coat has not been found. <hi rend="italic">The prisoner called</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
